<main class="jumbotron">
  <h1>File a report</h1>
</main>

<h4>PTV Lost Property Enquiries</h4>
<h4>
  <a href="tel:1800 800 007">
    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-earphone"></i>1800 800 007</a>
</h4>
<p>
  <small>(6am to midnight daily)</small><br>
  <span class="is_ptv_open">
    <span class="label label-success">PTV is open now</span>
  </span>
</p>

<hr>

<p>
  If an item is located and handed to PTV and/or Victoria Police and matches your report, you will be contacted via the details you have provided.
</p>

<form class="form-lost-property">
  <input class="form-control" placeholder="Name" type="text">
  <input class="form-control" placeholder="Email" type="email">
  <input class="form-control" placeholder="Item Name" type="name">
  <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Item Description" rows="3"></textarea>
  <p>Do you have a photo of the item?</p>
  <input accept="image/*" capture="camera" class="image-upload" id="capture" type="file">
  <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Submit report</button>
</form>

<hr>
